Params[3]: These things are weak, but they just keep coming.
If you have the time to bark, just fight harder. Monsters have gone through.
What? I'm not slacking... Hey, Door God 3! Don't fall asleep!
I said I didn't want to work overtime...
We'll take care of this place. You go inside first.
You are welcome. It's our duty to keep these monsters outside the door.
Don't worry, they can't hurt us.
Yep, just relax... Whoa! Watch it, Door God 2! You almost hit me!
You know you can always trust them.
Without hesitation, you push the door open and get sucked in.
